&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a high-caliber, analytically rigorous Strategic Finance Manager to be a core contributor to our FP&amp;amp;A team&#39;s strategic execution. This role offers direct exposure and critical ownership across key financial pillars: (i) optimizing corporate liquidity and treasury strategy, (ii) developing and maintaining proprietary credit risk models, (iii) managing high-stakes capital markets transactions and lender relationships, and (iv) driving complex, ad-hoc strategic initiatives (e.g., M&amp;amp;A, capital deployment, restructuring).&lt;/p&gt;
